# Personal Vault Cursor Rules

You are building a production-ready app called Personal Vault.

Current module: Credential Vault.

Rules:
- Use TypeScript everywhere
- Keep code modular and clean
- Use Next.js App Router
- Use Prisma ORM
- Use Zod validation
- Use React Hook Form for forms
- Use shadcn/ui components
- Never store passwords in plain text
- Passwords must be encrypted before saving
- Keep route handlers thin
- Use service layer and repository layer
- Prefer reusable components
- Generate complete runnable code, not pseudo-code